        {
            "title": "國際｜據報BBC將裁員最多2,000人",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"國際｜據報BBC將裁員最多2,000人\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZU5IM3jZZj4Rghx06ugxUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">國際｜據報BBC將裁員最多2,000人</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國廣播公司(BBC)周三宣布，計劃在未來兩年內裁員多達2000人，旨在節省年度預算的10%，即5億英鎊(約53.19億港元)。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這次在員工會議上宣布的裁員計劃，是這家英國國家廣播機構十多年來規模最大的一次。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">代理總裁Rhodri Talfan Davies在發給員工的郵件中表示，雖然這會帶來極大的不確定性，但公司必須公開面對挑戰。他指出，裁員的主因在於通貨膨脹、電視牌照費與商業收入的壓力，以及全球經濟的動盪。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4dd697e1-fc48-3b1d-82e8-311c9e9d909c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">BBC早前已表示面臨巨大的財務壓力，並計劃在2029年前削減約十分之一的預算，而大部分的削減措施將在2027年4月1日開始的財政年度內執行。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次削減時正值管理層更迭，前Google高層布里廷(Matt Brittin)預計於下個月出任總裁一職，接替去年因誤導性剪輯美國總統特朗普演講而辭職的戴維(Tim Davie)。特朗普正以誹謗為由，向BBC索償100億美元。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1bbc%E5%B0%87%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A2-000%E4%BA%BA-051829452.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 13:29:06",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "Trend Micro股價因與Anthropic網路安全合作而飆升",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Nvib4xSMzsyQIvZwgu7Dkw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAAG092_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 日本網路安全公司Trend Micro在週四宣布與<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"Anthropic\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:Anthropic;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/Anthropic\">Anthropic</a>合作,將整合其Claude人工智慧模型後,股價大幅上漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Trend Micro Inc. (TYO:4704)股價跳漲近12%至6,100.0日圓,成為日經225指數中表現最佳的股票之一,該指數當日跳漲逾2%創下歷史新高。Trend Micro股價一度觸及近三個月高點6,294.0日圓。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司的企業網路安全部門TrendAI宣布與Anthropic建立合作夥伴關係,共同研發AI代理自動化、AI原生安全營運,並開發旨在識別AI系統漏洞的系統。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2b5ca092-5e6f-3680-b05c-71ac7234994a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次合作正值投資者對AI相關網路安全關注度提升之際,特別是在Anthropic推出其Mythos AI模型之後,該公司聲稱該模型功能過於強大,因其能夠發現多個高嚴重性漏洞而不宜向公眾發布。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Anthropic已宣布啟動Glasswing專案,邀請主要科技公司、網路安全公司和華爾街頂級銀行評估該模型並準備適當的防禦措施。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/trend-micro%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%9B%A0%E8%88%87anthropic%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%8C%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87-051619284.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 13:20:06",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "聚焦對沖基金：看空美元；宏觀基金在華受創；Pershing啟動IPO路演",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以下為截至4月16日一周的<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"對沖基金\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:對沖基金;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/對沖基金\">對沖基金</a>相關要聞：</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">行業要聞</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對沖基金MS Capital稱獲得10億美元投資中國股票的委托</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">量化對沖基金Meridian &amp; Saturn Capital表示已獲得10億美元委托來交易中國股票，投資方為一家中東主權財富基金，該公司將採用市場中性策略交易中國境內股票。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">阿克曼為Pershing Square USA的IPO啟動路演 預計將於4月28日定價</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比爾·阿克曼正式啟動其封閉式基金和對沖基金在美國IPO的路演。根據彭博看到的條款，Pershing Square USA的IPO預計將於4月28日定價，融資規模可能高達100億美元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9dcaeec3-569a-3610-84eb-5eece8928d7c-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加密對沖基金轉戰原油等傳統資產 依托全天候區塊鏈平台交易</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">加密對沖基金如今正通過基於區塊鏈的平台交易原油、銅和那斯達克100指數等傳統資產，從定價低效中尋找獲利機會。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">少數大行主導對沖基金融資 標普警示金融穩定風險</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普全球警告稱，少數幾家銀行向對沖基金和自營交易公司提供數十億美元資金，以放大其押注，這一趨勢日益占據主導地位，正在帶來新的金融穩定風險。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Alua Capital Management將關閉其規模20億美元的對沖基金</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Alua Capital Management將在運營約五年後關閉其規模20億美元的對沖基金。儘管該基金曾有一段時間表現強勁，但公司認定其回報不足。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">交易策略</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美伊延長停火預期升溫 對沖基金愈發看空美元</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著美國與伊朗有望延長停火，對沖基金對美元越來越悲觀。摩根士丹利的交易模型顯示，截至4月10日，投資者本月以來進一步加大了看空美元的押注。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對沖基金在美、伊停火後通過選擇權押注韓元和人民幣走高</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國與伊朗停火的消息傳出後，隨著風險情緒改善和油價下跌，對沖基金乘機利用選擇權押注韓元和人民幣將走強。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">業績表現</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">宏觀對沖基金在中國遭受重創 備受追捧的橋水策略亦虧損5.6%</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於伊朗戰事攪動市場，宏觀對沖基金上個月在中國遭遇重創，就連十分搶手的橋水境內策略也不例外。彭博新聞社看到的淨值數據顯示，橋水的全天候增強基金在2月27日至4月3日期間下跌了5.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">D1 Capital股票組合3月大跌6% 重倉押注失利</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，Dan Sundheim執掌的D1 Capital Partners的股票投資組合3月下跌6%，成為當月表現最差的選股基金之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">明星宏觀交易員Rokos的對沖基金3月獲利 其他同行因中東戰事大多虧損</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管中東戰爭擾亂市場導致宏觀交易同行普遍遭受損失，但Chris Rokos的對沖基金3月仍實現約2.1%的回報率。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">倫敦對沖基金JJJ在3月動盪中虧損11% 而Kirkoswald同期盈利</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，倫敦對沖基金JJJ Capital Management上月虧損11.4%，抹去年內全部漲幅，而Greg Coffey旗下Kirkoswald Asset Management同月上漲0.23%，一季度回報率達到11%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">人事變動</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Bobby Jain旗下對沖基金從同行競爭對手挖角四名基金經理</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，Bobby Jain旗下多策略對沖基金從包括Hudson River Trading和Point72 Asset Management在內的競爭對手挖角四名基金經理。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%9A%E7%84%A6%E5%B0%8D%E6%B2%96%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91-%E7%9C%8B%E7%A9%BA%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83-%E5%AE%8F%E8%A7%80%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E5%9C%A8%E8%8F%AF%E5%8F%97%E5%89%B5-pershing%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95ipo%E8%B7%AF%E6%BC%94-041534488.html",
