        {
            "title": "黃金重返4800美元，白銀突破80美元大關！白銀市場醞釀擠倉行情",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周四，4月16日，美伊疑似考慮延長停火，黃金、白銀重拾升勢！XAU/USD上升0.71%，再次站上4800美元。LBMA董事總經理露絲·克勞威爾（Ruth Crowell）表示，黃金仍然是避險資產，仍然是儲備資產，在危機時刻它正在發揮自己的作用。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"583\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xXNLtzO51lz3_F.gKMxLSA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4Mw--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/bf5de059c577843515fa5f001c281973\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">XAG/USD升近2%%，突破80美元大關。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"576\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DkjDYh9TcALDGcIHRd5qHQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU3Ng--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/22ed252a1981a2b13a8b25fc4730c805\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《世界白銀調查》(World Silver Survey)預測，2026年，白銀市場將連續第六年出現供應缺口，總需求超出供應，今年白銀市場將出現約4600萬盎司的缺口。由於低庫存和連續六年的產量短缺為價格大幅變動創造了條件， 全球白銀市場已為又一次「擠倉」做好了鋪墊，可能推動價格飆升。<br/><br/></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong><u><span>財報季，美股數字睇到眼花？</span></u></strong> <strong><u><span>Warren AI</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>一鍵解讀數據！現在</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>InvestingPro</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>立享</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>50%</span></u></strong><strong><u><span>折扣，</span></u></strong> <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em><span>即刻點擊訂閱</span></em></strong></a><strong><u><span>！</span></u></strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><br/></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"772\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/J3rymmUrAlIsV4zxbsGACA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc3Mg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/investing_com_hk_986/2073d5df6efff753a893ca84af8a7588\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></blockquote></div>",
